name: AG Josh Shapiro
tweet: There may be more victims of Much. I encourage anyone with information to report it to the police. My Office listens to survivors and will follow every lead.  Victims or families can call Detective Sergeant George Moore at 610-566-8445.

name: AG Josh Shapiro
tweet: CONSUMER ALERT  Be careful when receiving calls or texts that claim to be about your taxes. Scammers often pose as the IRS to try and frighten consumers into giving away their personal info and $.   Keep yourself, your money, and your personal info safe.   https://t.co/LcGsNjQAzo
